{"type": "article", "id": 36353, "title": "用霓虹灯装饰房间，一种新式复古｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-01-03T23:12:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 28346, "name": "Joseph Joseph"}, {"id": 36427, "name": "Electric Confetti"}, {"id": 36428, "name": "Youmeus"}, {"id": 36429, "name": "Michał Kulesza"}, {"id": 36430, "name": "Alaa Amra"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 228, "image": "img/article/article_show/201701040019306GdmnlZrEW38c5yS.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Electric Confetti by Natalie Jarvis</h3><p>看到漂亮的霓虹灯招牌时，你有没有想过用它们装饰自己的房间？墨尔本灯饰设计公司 <a href=\"https://electricconfetti.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Electric Confetti</a> 由插画师 Natalie Jarvis 创立，用“通电的五彩纸屑”来形容旗下的灯饰再正确不过：它们用色鲜艳但并不刺目，造型大多取自日常生活中的物品或是流行文化符号。有点像是那种你会在派对上看到的装饰，点亮后房间的氛围似乎一下子就变得更加活泼了。你可以通过<a href=\"https://electricconfetti.com/collections/all\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到这些灯饰，售价从 149 澳元起。如果你觉得现有的灯饰画风并不适合自己，他们也提供定制服务。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104001949NuhfWkEz6nSlcUTv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104001949O4RAXQgLEDU9Kz26.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104001949UyuJPWN8TbmiOnC4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.582500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104001949ofBZLQVs2aAOmuNU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701040019498sKqaiXIQY4R6gw1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104001949wtZhnWFr7avLIqk5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Omelette Bowl by Youmeus</h3><p>虽然微波烹饪称得上是最简单快捷的下厨捷径，但专为这种烹饪方式打造的厨具并不常见。为了扩充自己的产品线，英国厨具品牌 <a href=\"https://www.josephjoseph.com/en-gb/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Joseph Joseph</a> 委托伦敦设计公司 <a href=\"http://www.youmeusdesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Youmeus</a> 设计了一套微波专用厨具，其中就包括这款蛋卷碗。设计师将平时煎欧姆蛋卷的平底锅和碗合二为一，利用自然倾斜的角度让打蛋液的过程变得更加轻松，餐后清洗时也只要洗一个碗就够了。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.josephjoseph.com/en-gb/m-cuisine-omelette-bowl\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 9 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104002005pUiKlOoJ3c04jVHA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104002005RqZKNvb1EYlD8osQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104002006LKhsqOrYQpdgePZN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104002005bh2uBCWSXjpGlntx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Sugar art by BIZE dessert studio</h3><p>大冬天窝在室内喝上一杯热饮是一件相当惬意的事，不过美国的乌克兰裔设计师 Lena Stacey 并不满足于此：热衷于“可食用设计”的她成立了一间名叫 BIZE 的甜品工作室，出售手工制作的蕾丝风格雕花糖片。这些精美的糖片放入热饮后会在两分钟左右融化，这个过程看着似乎就能感觉到甜蜜。你可以通过她的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/BIZEdessertstudio\" rel=\"nofollow\">网店</a>购买或者定制糖片，售价从 14.40 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104002024trgckiJjIasZ3G7H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.813846\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104002024BUVcLxQ4wbDh5ekg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.016923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104002024Sbp2FL0lfQRtU6ia.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.236923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Book clutch by BAGatelle Studio</h3><p>各式各样的书籍本身就为设计师们提供了不少启发，加上它们大多都是四四方方的造型，也不难理解为什么会有做成书的创意手拿包了。来自俄罗斯的 Elena Myloslavskaya 是一个热爱缝纫的设计师，在朋友的帮助下，她开设了名为 BAGatelle Studio 的工作室，利用人造革搭配印刷的方式制作手拿包。和我们曾经介绍的另一个<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/31956.html\">书籍手拿包</a>品牌相比，BAGatelle Studio 并不打算通过多元的材质和复杂的设计加工来吸引人们的注意力，整体的风格要低调很多。如果你感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/BAGatelleStudio\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买，售价为 78 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104002045xI6lFs1MwNDQ5kPG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104002045Jcw1v5xYaG2QV3pm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104002045fovKPN0su9XIbgkn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750877\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701040020450WVbKMxILu6rda49.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750877\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lego photography project by Michał Kulesza</h3><p>不少设计师和艺术家都会尝试所谓的“百日挑战”以激发自己的创造力，如果你觉得坚持三个多月的时间不重样已经很难的话，这套持续了近 250 天的<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/46271687/Lego-photo-project\" rel=\"nofollow\">乐高玩具摄影作品</a>会让你感叹波兰艺术家 <a href=\"http://trzyzmiany.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Michał Kulesza</a> 的脑洞。Kulesza 的这个项目分为两个部分：前 135 天说的是日常生活，积木在他手中变成了面包上的黄油、剃刀下的胡须或是他的领带；随后的 106 天中，他构思了一个自己变形为乐高人的故事，拍摄过半还有用锤子让自己的手恢复原样的剧情。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701040021407P0QjLyUxRed6fzX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104002140ayVQP5u3CepjAckE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104002140yW692nVvsiStK8Uz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104002140jOd7ezf8mMRWPspT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104002140wxeU17riDfLGWMQR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104002142I4gorMWDvJVE1uyF.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.370000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Aromatherapy by Alaa Amra</h3><p>为了强调手工打造这一特点，加拿大设计师 <a href=\"http://www.alaamra.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alaa Amra</a> 将肥皂制作过程中出现的最漂亮的一幕（加入颜料后产生类似大理石纹的效果）放在了手工皂品牌 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/45089023/Aromatherapy\" rel=\"nofollow\">Aromatherapy</a> 的包装上。由于肥皂分为昼夜两个系列，Amra 还采用了橙和蓝两种主色调，用不同比例的混合表现出七种不同的肥皂香型。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104002202ymBX8KUG0F6phRQP.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104002202qj5vocxDhImWnbYy.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104002201hPm2eHc4Oqb8XK9t.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104002202m7PHXTxvyhWeGtMd.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017010400220371QU9qpBfhMjlFsn.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}